    • Enum Constant Detail

      • FILE

        public static final MPQArchiveOpenFlags.BaseProvider FILE
        The MPQ is a local file. This is the default value.

      • MAP

        public static final MPQArchiveOpenFlags.BaseProvider MAP
        The MPQ is a local file. Stormlib will attempt to map the file into memory. This speeds up the MPQ operations (reading, verifying), but has size and operating system limitations.

      • HTTP

        public static final MPQArchiveOpenFlags.BaseProvider HTTP
        The MPQ is on a web server available via HTTP protocol. The server must support random access. Only supported in Windows.
